        "Title": "Unforgettable Pale Blue",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131634227889",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ee64e127-98ed-4049-8b7f-e0e1d7676c1d).Image",
        "Description": "A detective lies in wake from a textbook murder.\r\rA famous lawyer was choked out under the rainy night in her attorney office. Foul play was involved, of course. Her fingernails contained blue fibre, a drink spilled on the floor contained sleeping medication, her death made way for others to move up the social ladder. While the justice system never incriminated everyone, he suffers from chronic insomnia and night terrors.\r\rThe detective will never forget that unforgettable pale blue.",
